Subject: RE: [T2] Valve Adjusting Screw

Remove the Rocker arm assembly(two nuts) remove and replace the adjuster. 
Check the condition of the others might be a good time to do those as well. 
When you replace it make sure to put all washers shims seals etc. back where 
they came from.



Michael Knight
'77 Westy Deluxe, "el Verde"





